---
// No props needed for this component
---

<section id="how-we-work" class="py-20 px-6 bg-white relative">
  <!-- Background Elements -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_30%_20%,rgba(23,72,252,0.05),transparent)] pointer-events-none"
  ></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative">
    <div class="text-center mb-16" data-aos="fade-up">
      <!-- <span class="text-gray-900 font-medium">كيف نعمل؟</span> -->
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mt-2 mb-6 text-black font-bold">كيف نعمل؟</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        نؤمن أن بناء منتج رقمي ناجح لا يعتمد فقط على البرمجة، بل على التعاون
        الوثيق، والتخطيط الذكي، والاستماع الدقيق.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Interactive Process Steps -->
    <div class="relative">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-8">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div
          class="work-step relative"
          data-aos="fade-up"
          data-aos-delay="0"
        >
          <div
            class="bg-gray-25 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 group border border-accent/20 h-full flex flex-col"
          >
            <div
              class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto relative group cursor-pointer hover:from-primary/10 hover:to-primary/30 transition-all duration-300"
            >
              <div
                class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gray-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center absolute -top-2 -right-2 transform group-hover:rotate-12 transition-transform duration-300 text-sm"
              >
                1
              </div>
              <i
                class="ri-customer-service-line ri-xl text-gray-900 transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"
              ></i>
            </div>
            <h3
              class="text-lg font-bold mb-4 text-center group-hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300 text-gray-900 leading-tight min-h-[3.5rem] flex items-center justify-center"
            >
              الاستماع والتحليل
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-center text-sm flex-grow">
              نبدأ بالاستماع لفكرتك وتحليلها بعمق، لفهم احتياجاتك وأهدافك بشكل دقيق
            </p>
            <div
              class="h-1 w-0 bg-primary mt-4 mx-auto group-hover:w-1/2 transition-all duration-500"
            ></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div
          class="work-step relative"
          data-aos="fade-up"
          data-aos-delay="100"
        >
          <div
            class="bg-gray-25 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 group border border-accent/20 h-full flex flex-col"
          >
            <div
              class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto relative group cursor-pointer hover:from-primary/10 hover:to-primary/30 transition-all duration-300"
            >
              <div
                class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gray-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center absolute -top-2 -right-2 transform group-hover:rotate-12 transition-transform duration-300 text-sm"
              >
                2
              </div>
              <i
                class="ri-flow-chart ri-xl text-gray-900 transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"
              ></i>
            </div>
            <h3
              class="text-lg font-bold mb-4 text-center group-hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300 text-gray-900 leading-tight min-h-[3.5rem] flex items-center justify-center"
            >
              التخطيط والتصميم
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-center text-sm flex-grow">
              نضع خطة تنفيذ واضحة ومقسّمة على مراحل، مع تصميم تجربة مستخدم
              مميزة
            </p>
            <div
              class="h-1 w-0 bg-primary mt-4 mx-auto group-hover:w-1/2 transition-all duration-500"
            ></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div
          class="work-step relative"
          data-aos="fade-up"
          data-aos-delay="200"
        >
          <div
            class="bg-gray-25 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 group border border-accent/20 h-full flex flex-col"
          >
            <div
              class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto relative group cursor-pointer hover:from-primary/10 hover:to-primary/30 transition-all duration-300"
            >
              <div
                class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gray-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center absolute -top-2 -right-2 transform group-hover:rotate-12 transition-transform duration-300 text-sm"
              >
                3
              </div>
              <i
                class="ri-code-box-line ri-xl text-gray-900 transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"
              ></i>
            </div>
            <h3
              class="text-lg font-bold mb-4 text-center group-hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300 text-gray-900 leading-tight min-h-[3.5rem] flex items-center justify-center"
            >
              التطوير والبرمجة
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-center text-sm flex-grow">
              نقوم بالتطوير البرمجي باستخدام أحدث التقنيات وأفضل الممارسات
            </p>
            <div
              class="h-1 w-0 bg-primary mt-4 mx-auto group-hover:w-1/2 transition-all duration-500"
            ></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4 -->
        <div
          class="work-step relative"
          data-aos="fade-up"
          data-aos-delay="300"
        >
          <div
            class="bg-gray-25 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 group border border-accent/20 h-full flex flex-col"
          >
            <div
              class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto relative group cursor-pointer hover:from-primary/10 hover:to-primary/30 transition-all duration-300"
            >
              <div
                class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gray-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center absolute -top-2 -right-2 transform group-hover:rotate-12 transition-transform duration-300 text-sm"
              >
                4
              </div>
              <i
                class="ri-test-tube-line ri-xl text-gray-900 transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"
              ></i>
            </div>
            <h3
              class="text-lg font-bold mb-4 text-center group-hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300 text-gray-900 leading-tight min-h-[3.5rem] flex items-center justify-center"
            >
              الاختبار والتحسين
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-center text-sm flex-grow">
              نجري اختبارات مكثفة لضمان الجودة والأداء الأمثل للمنتج
            </p>
            <div
              class="h-1 w-0 bg-primary mt-4 mx-auto group-hover:w-1/2 transition-all duration-500"
            ></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 5 -->
        <div
          class="work-step relative"
          data-aos="fade-up"
          data-aos-delay="400"
        >
          <div
            class="bg-gray-25 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 group border border-accent/20 h-full flex flex-col"
          >
            <div
              class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto relative group cursor-pointer hover:from-primary/10 hover:to-primary/30 transition-all duration-300"
            >
              <div
                class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gray-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center absolute -top-2 -right-2 transform group-hover:rotate-12 transition-transform duration-300 text-sm"
              >
                5
              </div>
              <i
                class="ri-rocket-line ri-xl text-gray-900 transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"
              ></i>
            </div>
            <h3
              class="text-lg font-bold mb-4 text-center group-hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300 text-gray-900 leading-tight min-h-[3.5rem] flex items-center justify-center"
            >
              الإطلاق
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-center text-sm flex-grow">
              نطلق المنتج بعد التأكد من جاهزيته وتوافقه مع المتطلبات
            </p>
            <div
              class="h-1 w-0 bg-primary mt-4 mx-auto group-hover:w-1/2 transition-all duration-500"
            ></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 6 -->
        <div
          class="work-step relative"
          data-aos="fade-up"
          data-aos-delay="500"
        >
          <div
            class="bg-gray-25 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 group border border-accent/20 h-full flex flex-col"
          >
            <div
              class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto relative group cursor-pointer hover:from-primary/10 hover:to-primary/30 transition-all duration-300"
            >
              <div
                class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gray-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center absolute -top-2 -right-2 transform group-hover:rotate-12 transition-transform duration-300 text-sm"
              >
                6
              </div>
              <i
                class="ri-customer-service-2-line ri-xl text-gray-900 transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300"
              ></i>
            </div>
            <h3
              class="text-lg font-bold mb-4 text-center group-hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300 text-gray-900 leading-tight min-h-[3.5rem] flex items-center justify-center"
            >
              المتابعة والدعم
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-center text-sm flex-grow">
              نقدم متابعة مستمرة ودعم فني متواصل بعد إطلاق المنتج
            </p>
            <div
              class="h-1 w-0 bg-primary mt-4 mx-auto group-hover:w-1/2 transition-all duration-500"
            ></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 